{"Name":"Duet@Emily","ShortName":"Duet@Emily","Description":"Duet@Emily is a freehold residential development by ZACD Group Limited, consisting of 3 adjoining 3-storey blocks beside the lush greenery of Mount Emily Park. This project has a land size of 5,549 sqft and is expected to have 20 units. Residents will enjoy close proximity to the CBD, Orchard Road and Dhoby Ghaut, as well as other major lifestyle destinations such as Plaza Singapura or 313 Somerset.","StartUrl":"/","Display":"standalone","BackgroundColor":"#ffffff","ThemeColor":"#041e42","Orientation":"portrait","Icons":[{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/a7dc64bf-d378-4e06-9910-cd8171de1f1b","Sizes":"192x192","Type":"image/png"},{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/a7dc64bf-d378-4e06-9910-cd8171de1f1b","Sizes":"512x512","Type":"image/png"}]}